msg: Creating a repository location for the Woden PGP KEYS file. This is the master public keys file which will accompany post-M7 milestones/releases.
Woden committers may append their public keys according to http://www.apache.org/dev/release-signing.html#keys-policy, that is,
(For example, using GnuPG: export the signature with "gpg --list-sigs" and the public key with "gpg --armor --export")
